WorkItem.Summary: [LoadCharacter] Unable to load any of my characters from "Load from Character Profile" option

Comments.Message:
Did you not read the errors themselves?

(407) Proxy Authentication Required.

That means you need to set up your proxy info in Rawr.
Did setting your Proxy Info fix it?
